{"tid":35151,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人經過見到公公婆婆乞錢都會比？","createTime":"2016-12-12T01:44:40.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T05:07:42.000Z","uid":26018,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0180d617aec87cc765e98339dd0a5604ef54c8be","tid":35151,"uid":26018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T01:44:40.000Z","msg":"我次次經過都會比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為佢地坐左成日，一定好攰<br />\n冬天或者落雨我會比多啲<br />\n因為真係辛苦錢黎<br />\n但前日見到成日係我經過個到乞錢既婆婆<br />\n當我諗住比錢既時候<br />\n見到佢渣住支萬寶露係到食<br />\n之後我比到錢佢<br />\n我驚我咁做會害左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2f2569e4ca76ac8f0132c240f89c9c7633e397b","tid":35151,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T01:57:29.000Z","msg":"唔會比<br />\n<br />\n一來唔知係唔係蝗<br />\n<br />\n二來扮窮既越來越多"},{"pid":"5f8e93bb17624d5f93183265e996855721652507","tid":35151,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T02:25:18.000Z","msg":"死老野早日訓棺材啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c5e78283837cbe45819687cc730093584ddc5c6","tid":35151,"uid":31368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T21:14:17.000Z","msg":"買野食，唔會比錢"},{"pid":"0b7d6e1588bd38e7496ee9d4e7618c837f222677","tid":35151,"uid":8726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T21:48:58.000Z","msg":"乞衣都食萬寶路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食大陸煙食撚死佢啦"},{"pid":"cf8351b759ce6b491f71f720af514a565ee3fb06","tid":35151,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T23:02:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f14b79294eed0d18777bbb7c85ed6e16032ccbe8","tid":35151,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T23:03:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a0cba6e9562ea27c51b26ec6c5d45ef